property.title: Santorini Apartment
property.description: Offering a balcony or patio with views of the mountain and city, the units feature air conditioning, a seating area, cable flat-screen TV and kitchen. The apartment complex provides some units that have a safety deposit box, and each unit has a private bathroom and a wardrobe. At the apartment complex, units have bed linen and towels.
